description: I have been creating generative art since 2010 using proprietary algorithms. This piece is one of the many directions I have discovered.  — This “Digital Stitch” is the result of a large number of boundaries being woven. Incidentally, this is something I arrived at during my work on the theme of “worms that can hear music”. So this is the inside of an earthworm. ...Have you ever seen a dancing worm?  - Qubibi ( more info https://www.notion.so/hello-NFT-Arts-f1ac45397c3342b19a4599b8f5a3af81 )
